              "free_text": [
                " The gamma-ray spectrum in coincidence with",
                "the spontaneous fission of 252Cf was measured with a",
                "NaI(Tl) spectrometer and an ionization chamber. Care",
                "was taken to correct for or to eliminate the",
                "simultaneous detection of two or more gamma rays per",
                "fission event. For this reason the gamma-ray",
                "detection efficiency was limited to 0.5%."
